                                        <p id="line1552"><br /> <a name="_ftn181"> </a> <a href="#_ftnref181"><sup>[181]</sup></a> Vgl. [Anon.], „Report of the Committee Upon a National Hymn”, in: <em>Dwight's Journal of Music</em> 19/21 (24. August 1861), S. 166.</p>
